OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother mostly dry and bright
OL,6,Fday and becoming hot, especially in
OL,7,Fthe south. Some rain for a time over
OL,8,Fnorth Argyll with some mist and sea
OL,9,Ffog around the Islands.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will stay dry through the
OL,12,Fevening and overnight with some
OL,13,Fevening sunshine but becoming
OL,14,Fincreasingly cloudy through the
OL,15,Fevening and overnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FA largely cloudy start.
OL,18,FStaying quite cloudy for many, with
OL,19,Fthe best of the sunshine on the west
OL,20,Fcoast. Still warm but a bit less so
OL,21,Fthan recent days.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
