OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fstart Sunday then brightening up with
OL,7,Fsunny intervals. Monday and Tuesday
OL,8,Fdry and sunny. Very warm in the west.
